    body: 'The baseline. Your d100 lands **at or under the skill value** as written on the sheet.\n\nA **Regular** success is the default the Keeper asks for. It means the task is done, competently, with no particular flourish — the lock opens, the reference is found, the shot connects.\n\nA Regular success also **marks the skill** for improvement at the end of the scenario, which is the only way most skills ever grow.',
