    body: 'An **Extreme** success needs the roll at or under **one fifth** of your skill, rounding down. Firearms (Handgun) 60 gives an Extreme range of **01–12**.\n\nThe Keeper sets Extreme difficulty for tasks near the edge of possibility. It also matters mechanically in combat: an Extreme success with an **impaling** weapon does **maximum damage plus a rolled damage die**, and an Extreme success on a manoeuvre or an opposed roll beats any lesser success.\n\nIf your skill is under 5, its Extreme value rounds to 0 and an Extreme success is simply impossible — the fifth is not "at least 1".',
